Anyway, this is Stefan, er...

01:33:30.200 --> 01:33:31.560
Butler, Butler.

01:33:34.480 --> 01:33:35.720
I'm Colin, yeah.

01:33:36.440 --> 01:33:39.240
Yeah, I've played all of your games.
All of them.

01:33:39.320 --> 01:33:42.640
Except the Commodore ones,
I don't have a Commodore.

