01:40:04.920 --> 01:40:06.480
To get in to the flow.

01:40:08.360 --> 01:40:09.520
Oh, music?

01:40:12.560 --> 01:40:15.400
Er, compilations mainly.

01:40:16.760 --> 01:40:17.760
Get a pen.

