-I said no.
-You said "no"?

01:42:21.840 --> 01:42:23.240
Well, not to the whole thing,

01:42:23.320 --> 01:42:25.880
just to working there
and being under their control.

01:42:26.640 --> 01:42:27.800
I don't know where it came from,

01:42:27.880 --> 01:42:29.920
I just said "no"
and then had to justify it

01:42:30.000 --> 01:42:32.120
by saying that I prefer to work alone.

01:42:33.840 --> 01:42:36.760
